PN,38601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FJersey residents could be forced to
OL,7,Fpay double for their water bills if
OL,8,Fproposed plans to reduce PFAS levels
OL,9,Fin the island's supply go ahead.
OL,11,FIt comes after Jersey Water says plans
OL,12,Fto lower the 'forever chemicals' from
OL,13,F12 nanograms to four could cost up to
OL,14,F#210 million, despite experts
OL,15,Fconfirming the supply is currently
OL,16,Fsafe.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FThe utility company's Chief Executive,
OL,7,FHelier Smith, says: "Jersey Water
OL,8,Freally wants to do everything we can
OL,9,Fto keep our bills as low as possible
OL,10,Fand to do that we really need to
OL,11,Funderstand the cost implications of
OL,12,Fthis limit before it comes in."
OL,14,FWhilst Jersey Water's PFAS levels are
OL,15,Fdeemed safe, a scientific panel
OL,16,Frecommended bringing the amount down
OL,17,Fto four nanograms per litre in
OL,18,FFebruary 2026, a limit the Environment
OL,19,FMinister wants to reach within five
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FDeputy Steve Luce has laid that out in
OL,7,Fa proposition to the States, but the
OL,8,Futility firm argues it needs at least
OL,9,Fseven years.
OL,11,FMr Smith adds: "Water in Jersey is
OL,12,Fsafe, the scientific panel has
OL,13,Fconcluded.
OL,15,F"It has confirmed that there's no
OL,16,Fcause for concern and that the
OL,17,Fproposed limit of PFAS included in
OL,18,Fthis proposition is precautionary, and
OL,19,Fthat's future proof, rather than to
OL,20,Faddress any concerns around the
OL,21,Fcurrent water levels."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FHe explains they have been trialing
OL,7,Fdifferent methods to reduce PFAS in
OL,8,FJersey's water supply.
OL,10,FMr Smith says: "Over the last 12
OL,11,Fmonths, we have been testing and
OL,12,Fassessing the feasibility of over 10
OL,13,Fdifferent treatment solutions, and we
OL,14,Fhave currently reached the consensus
OL,15,Fthat to reach the four nanograms per
OL,16,Flimit, there is only one long-term
OL,17,Ftreatment solution which is suitable
OL,18,Fand that is using granular activted
OL,19,Fcarbon and iron exchange at a new
OL,20,Ffacility somewhere else other than
OL,21,Fthis treatment works.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"We are also looking at liquid
OL,7,Fpowdered activated carbon, which will
OL,8,Fonly be viable as an interim solution
OL,9,Fbecause we don't expect it to hit the
OL,10,Ffour nanograms, but that could provide
OL,11,Fa realistic way of meaningfully
OL,12,Freducing the amount of PFAS in our
OL,13,Fwater. We are already at safe levels,
OL,14,Fbut getting closer towards the four.
OL,16,F"To meet the levels, we are looking at
OL,17,Fa cost in the range of #140 to #210
OL,18,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"Based on the work we have done so
OL,7,Ffar, that would include the creation
OL,8,Fof a new treatment facility somewhere
OL,9,Felse in the island dedicated to
OL,10,Ftreating PFAS."
OL,12,FWhat is PFAS?
OL,14,FPerfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl
OL,15,Fsubstances - or as they are more
OL,16,Fcommonly known, PFAS - are a group of
OL,17,Fmanmade chemicals that resist breaking
OL,18,Fdown in the environment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FThey were first developed for
OL,7,Findustrial use in the 1940s, but
OL,8,Fduring the 60s and 70s became commonly
OL,9,Fused in everything from carpets to
OL,10,Fcleaning agents, sprays and paints to
OL,11,Ftextiles and hydraulic fluid.
OL,13,FThe chemical remains in the body, and
OL,14,Fsome studies have linked it to certain
OL,15,Ftypes of cancer.
OL,17,FPFAS and PFOS: What is the difference?
OL,19,FPFAS and Jersey:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FPFAS is present in the island-wide
OL,7,Fwater supply, although it is within
OL,8,Flimits set by the UK and EU.
OL,10,FIt was concluded in 2022 that there
OL,11,Fwere 'higher than expected' levels of
OL,12,FPFAS in the blood samples of islanders
OL,13,Fliving in Jersey following Government-
OL,14,Fbacked testing of 72 people from 31
OL,15,Faddresses very close to Jersey Airport.
OL,17,FThe 'forever chemicals' leaked into
OL,18,Fprivate borehole water supplies after
OL,19,Fit was used in firefighting foams
OL,20,Fduring a training day at Jersey
OL,21,FAirport in 1991.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FIn February 2026, Jersey's health
OL,7,Fdepartment announced it would offer
OL,8,Fmedical treatment to residents who
OL,9,Flived in affected areas at the time,
OL,10,Fsuch as St Ouens, around Jersey
OL,11,FAirport and Upper Pont Marquet, with
OL,12,Felevated levels of PFAS in their blood
OL,13,F- alongside additional testing for at-
OL,14,Frisk groups.
OL,16,FHowever, the water utility firm says
OL,17,Fto meet the proposed limit the company
OL,18,Fcannot afford the cost alone.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FMr Smith explains: "It will require
OL,7,Fnew government funding, and it's
OL,8,Freally important that States Members
OL,9,Funderstand the implications of this
OL,10,Ffour-nanogram limit, against the cost
OL,11,Fof a new treatment facility and also
OL,12,Fthe impact on customer bills.
OL,14,F"If the work that we are doing
OL,15,Findicates that we need a new treatment
OL,16,Ffacility, which costs up to #210
OL,17,Fmillion, it's possible that bills
OL,18,Fcould need to increase by 70 to 110%,
OL,19,Fwhich is a significant increase, and
OL,20,Fwe need to do everything we possibly
OL,21,Fcan to make sure that doesn't happen.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"That is why additional information is
OL,7,Frequired to understand the
OL,8,Fconsequences of this four-nanogram
OL,9,Flimit, so we will do everything within
OL,10,Four power to keep the costs for the
OL,11,Fisland and for our customers as low as
OL,12,Freasonably possible.
OL,14,F"We have indicated to the Government
OL,15,Fthat we will require support to fund
OL,16,Fit, so this proposal needs to really
OL,17,Fconsider the cost, where that money is
OL,18,Fcoming from and how the Government can
OL,19,Fsupport Jersey Water to deliver the
OL,20,Ftechnical requirements of PFAS
OL,21,Ftreatments.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"We are potentially setting a limit to
OL,7,Fthe island that doesn't know how it's
OL,8,Fgoing to pay for or the cost."
OL,10,FDr Sabine Donnai, a health management
OL,11,Fexpert based in the UK, adds: "Toxins
OL,12,Fon their own, if you were to just take
OL,13,Fone PFAS and say, 'Is it going to give
OL,14,Fme thyroid cancer?' Unlikely, unless
OL,15,Fyou have really high levels.
OL,17,F"But it is the multitude of toxins
OL,18,Fthat we are in contact with that is
OL,19,Faffecting our health."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Environment, Housing
OL,7,Fand Infrastructure Hearing on 3 March,
OL,8,Fthe Environment Minister, Deputy Luce,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Given that we made a commitment
OL,10,Fto do something about PFAS within my
OL,11,Ftwo-year period, given it was quite a
OL,12,Fshort ministerial period, I took the
OL,13,Fdecision to lodge the proposition, and
OL,14,Fwe will see what happens."
OL,16,FIn a statement, he continued:
OL,17,F"Independent experts have examined
OL,18,Fthis issue thoroughly, and their
OL,19,Frecommendations are grounded in
OL,20,Fscience and public engagement.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"My role is to ensure these findings
OL,7,Fare brought forward clearly and
OL,8,Ftransparently. In doing so, I will
OL,9,Fcontinue discussing all relevant
OL,10,Fmatters with ministerial colleagues
OL,11,Fand the Scrutiny Panel, and
OL,12,Fultimately, the States Assembly is the
OL,13,Fright forum for the debate."
OL,15,FJersey's Treasury Minister, Deputy
OL,16,FElaine Millar, adds: "I want to
OL,17,Freassure islanders that the Council of
OL,18,FMinisters is treating this issue as a
OL,19,Fpriority and has already held
OL,20,Fdiscussions on the matter.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"Jersey Water presently meets EU and
OL,7,FUK standards for water quality and
OL,8,FPFAS, which I know will be reassuring
OL,9,Fto many. The Council of Ministers is
OL,10,Fgrateful for the panel's advice and
OL,11,Faccepts its recommendation on future
OL,12,FPFAS levels in water.
OL,14,F"We will, however, need to assess the
OL,15,Fpace at which any changes can be
OL,16,Fdelivered to ensure they are both
OL,17,Feffective and affordable.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772791513
OL,3,CWarning bills could double to reduce
OL,4,Cchemicals in water supply
OL,6,F"It is important that we consider both
OL,7,Fthe cost-of-living pressures many
OL,8,Fislanders are facing, as well as the
OL,9,Fwider financial implications for
OL,10,FGovernment and for Jersey Water.
OL,12,F"I am reviewing the current proposal
OL,13,Fand considering an amendment that
OL,14,Fwould support a balanced and
OL,15,Fresponsible approach for the island,
OL,16,Fwhich allows us to move to the
OL,17,Frecommended limit within a realistic
OL,18,Ftimeframe."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
